column2: SELECT TOP # sp.objID,  sp.ra,  sp.dec, sp.plateID AS plateID, sp.plate AS plate,  sp.mjd AS mjd, sp.fiberID AS fiberID, sp.z AS Z, sp.zErr AS Z_Err, sp.psfmag_u, sp.psfmag_g, sp.psfmag_r, sp.psfmag_i, sp.psfmag_z FROM specPhotoALL AS sp  JOIN galSpecExtra AS gse ON (sp.specObjID = gse.specObjID) WHERE  zWarning = # AND ((Z > #) AND (Z < #)) ORDER BY Z
